<section id="clock">
<title>Clock, calendar and location</title>
<media type="image" src="figures/mate-clock-prefs-general.png"
       width="250" height="141" style="floatright">
  <p>Clock, calendar, and location</p>
</media>

<p>Click the clock one right of the top panel to see the current date,
a month-by-month calendar, and a list of your locations. Modifying your
settings is as easy as a right-click. An extensive set of locations
is available. You can adjust Weather wind speed measurement and
temperature display as well.</p>

