<section id="yourname">
<title>You and your computer</title>

<media type="image" src="figures/mate-control-center.png"
       width="250" height="160" style="floatright">
  <p>Control Center</p>
</media>

<p>Click <em>System</em> then <em>Preferences</em> then
   <em>About me</em> in the Menu top panel to manage your profile.</p>

<p>You can quickly access almost all of your computer needs for
Preferences in the <em>Control Center</em>. Settings for file sharing,
keyboard and any number of other preferences are available with this
simple method from the main menu: Click <em>System</em>::<em>Control
Center</em>.</p>

<p>There is a <em>Notification Area</em> in the top panel just to the
left of the system Clock. That area varies in size for the
<em>Notification</em> aware applications and applets to have a standard
location to announce various events. One example is if on a laptop when
your battery is critically low.</p>

